<title><%= title %></title>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-10 sm:py-14 md:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 fade-in">
    <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-14">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/8 dark:bg-primary/15 text-primary text-xs font-bold mb-4">
            <i class="ph-bold ph-star"></i> Fitur Unggulan
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-secondary dark:text-white mb-4">Yang Bisa Anda Lakukan</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">Eksplorasi ekosistem PuZero — platform serba guna yang dirancang untuk produktivitas digital Anda.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-5 stagger">
        <div class="animate-slide-up feature-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/60 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md dark:hover:shadow-slate-900/50">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-primary/8 dark:bg-primary/15 text-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 cat-icon">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-lightning text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white mb-2">AI Chat Performa Tinggi</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Gunakan model Gemini 3 Flash terbaru untuk membantu coding, menulis artikel, atau sekadar teman ngobrol yang cerdas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up feature-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/60 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md dark:hover:shadow-slate-900/50">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-pink-500/8 dark:bg-pink-500/15 text-pink-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 cat-icon">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-instagram-logo text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white mb-2">Downloader Media Cepat</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Unduh video Reels, foto, dan konten TikTok tanpa watermark dalam hitungan detik dengan kualitas original.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up feature-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/60 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md dark:hover:shadow-slate-900/50">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-indigo-500/8 dark:bg-indigo-500/15 text-indigo-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 cat-icon">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-layout text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white mb-2">Modern & SPA-like</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Navigasi antar halaman terasa sangat cepat tanpa reload penuh berkat integrasi teknologi HTMX.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up feature-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/60 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md dark:hover:shadow-slate-900/50">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-emerald-500/8 dark:bg-emerald-500/15 text-emerald-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 cat-icon">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-shield-check text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white mb-2">Privasi & Keamanan</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Semua riwayat chat disimpan secara lokal di browser Anda. Kami tidak menyimpan data sensitif di server kami.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up feature-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/60 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md dark:hover:shadow-slate-900/50">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-amber-500/8 dark:bg-amber-500/15 text-amber-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 cat-icon">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-image text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white mb-2">AI Image Tools</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Tingkatkan resolusi gambar dengan AI Upscale atau ubah foto menjadi gaya anime Ghibli yang indah.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up feature-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/60 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md dark:hover:shadow-slate-900/50">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-rose-500/8 dark:bg-rose-500/15 text-rose-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 cat-icon">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-moon-stars text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-secondary dark:text-white mb-2">Dark Mode Elegan</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Nikmati pengalaman visual yang nyaman dengan tema gelap yang otomatis menyesuaikan preferensi sistem Anda.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a hx-get="/category" hx-target="#main-content" hx-push-url="true"
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer px-7 py-3.5 bg-secondary dark:bg-primary text-white rounded-2xl font-black text-sm hover:bg-slate-700 dark:hover:opacity-90 transition-all shadow-lg active:scale-95 btn-hover-effect">
            Coba Semua Fitur <i class="ph-bold ph-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
